Before sending data TCP establish a 3 way handshake:

    Step-1:
        Syn (synchronize)
            In this user sends a request to server that i want to establish TCP connection

    Step-2:
        Ack-Syn(Acknowledgments-synchronize)
            In this server says "I received your request and i am ready"
            and expects or wait for data from client

    Step-3:
        Ack
            In this client confirm the connection and sends data


