Solution is WebSocket(Connection protocol) :

In this we open one connection and does not close it
by the help of this server can send response anytime and client can also share anytime
in the same connection
Server and client reuses the same connection
-> real time

A WebSocket API makes it possible to make/create a two way interactive connection session between user and server
In this way we does not have to poll the server for request

A Websocket request is a normal http request only with
specialized headers ->
The important headers are:

Upgrade: websocket → "I want to switch from HTTP to WebSocket."
Connection: Upgrade → "Upgrade this connection."
Sec-WebSocket-Key → Random key used during the handshake.
Sec-WebSocket-Version → WebSocket protocol version.

its status code is 101


WebSocket is implemented on both frontend  and backend side
A WebSocket has two endpoints
1.frontend -> which is responsible for opening websocket connection and send and receive messages
2.backend -> it is responsible for accepting the connection , processes messages and send response



